<br>
Two weeks later, the drop rate was nerfed to what it is today, and shrooms no longer dropped spells, only the harder mobs in the zone did.<br>
<br>
Three weeks later, Australia received it's first copies of the Luclin expansion.<br>
<br>
By changing drop rates on items/spells to be high immediately after the expansion, and lower after a week or two, you penalyze those who can't obtain the expansion, especially those in Europe and Australasia.<br>
<br>
I suspect that the spells are able to be obtained through other means, but we have not yet discovered how.  I have also sat listening to magicians in the Serverwide.Magetower channel talk about their travels through PoP (No, Australia still doesn't have it) and link to 4 or 5 spells, or the items they have summoned.  <br>
<br>
